OL,3,C'Simulation' glasses help recreate
OL,4,Cexperience of visually impaired
OL,6,FJulia Barthram joined a guided walk
OL,7,Fthrough Newcastle which recreated the
OL,8,Fexperience of living with a visual
OL,9,Fimpairment
OL,11,F'Simulation spectacles' helped
OL,12,Frecreate the experience of living with
OL,13,Fa visual impairment on a guided walk
OL,14,Fthrough Newcastle.
OL,16,FCouncil officers were taken on the
OL,17,Fwalk with the aim of highlighting the
OL,18,Fdifficulties faced by people living
OL,19,Fwith sight impairments on a daily
OL,20,Fbasis in the city centre.
