OL,3,C'Simulation' glasses help recreate
OL,4,Cexperience of visually impaired
OL,6,FAs part of a guided walk by Tyne and
OL,7,FWear Sight Loss Council (SLC), the
OL,8,Fgroup wore 'simulation spectacles'
OL,9,Fwhich gave them an idea of what it is
OL,10,Flike to live with different visual
OL,11,Fimpairments.
OL,13,FJack Moffat is the engagement manager
OL,14,Ffor Tyne and Wear SLC and said he has
OL,15,Fhis own experience struggling with
OL,16,Fnavigating the city centre.
OL,18,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees: "As a white
OL,19,Fcane user myself, I have struggled to
OL,20,Fnavigate the streets in the city
OL,21,Fcentre of Newcastle.
