OL,3,C'Simulation' glasses help recreate
OL,4,Cexperience of visually impaired
OL,6,F"I often bump into advertising boards
OL,7,Fblocking the pavement with my cane and
OL,8,Fhave tripped over e-scooters that have
OL,9,Fbeen left outside of shops.
OL,11,F"This creates a fear of going out to
OL,12,Fdo the everyday things that others can
OL,13,Fdo without stress. I want to be able
OL,14,Fto access Newcastle city centre
OL,15,Fwithout fear and enjoy the wonderful
OL,16,Fcity that I am so proud of."
OL,18,FThere are more than 36,800 blind and
OL,19,Fpartially sighted people live in the
OL,20,Farea, according to Tyne and Wear SLC.
