OL,3,C'Simulation' glasses help recreate
OL,4,Cexperience of visually impaired
OL,6,FObstacles for those with forms of
OL,7,Fsight loss can include advertising
OL,8,Fboards, outdoor furniture, e-scooters
OL,9,Fand uneven paving.
OL,11,FMr Moffatt continued: "Our joint goal
OL,12,Fis to make Newcastle streets and the
OL,13,Flocal environment accessible by
OL,14,Fremoving barriers for blind and
OL,15,Fpartially sighted people, so everyone
OL,16,Fcan live the lives they want to live
OL,17,Fin an equal way."
OL,19,FNewcastle City Council said it would
OL,20,Ftake forward any issues highlighted
OL,21,Ffrom the walk for future plans.
