OL,6,FChristine Herriot, director of city
OL,7,Foperations, neighbourhoods and
OL,8,Fregulatory services, said: "Obviously
OL,9,Fwe've got a duty of care for our
OL,10,Fresidents and visitors, for anything
OL,11,Fthat's going on the highway.
OL,13,F"Whether it's utility works or
OL,14,Fcontractors, or whether it's pavement
OL,15,Fcafes, we've got to make sure it's
OL,16,Faccessible for people who use our
OL,17,Fhighways.
