OL,6,F"We do consider accessibility in
OL,7,Feverything we do. We're always welcome
OL,8,Fto hear from people's issues and try
OL,9,Fand improve as much as possible. We
OL,10,Fwill look at this and try and
OL,11,Fincorporate any issues they highlight
OL,12,Finto any future designs."
OL,14,FThe walk was supported by the Royal
OL,15,FNational Institute of Blind People
OL,16,F(RNIB), Newcastle Vision Support and
OL,17,FNorth East Sight Matters
OL,18,FRehabilitation Officers.
